        <item>
          <updateDate>2013-02-05T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Donate for Disaster Relief Act of 2013 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow individual taxpayers to designate an amount (not less than $1) of any overpayment of income tax to a Disaster Relief Fund, established by this Act, for the purpose of providing relief for major disasters declared under the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2013-02-05</actionDate>
